msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome the the setup wizard of your new Freifunk Münsterland node. Please fill out the following form and transmit it."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:macaddr"
msgstr ""
"<p>This is your Freifunk node's public key. The node won't be able to connect to the mesh VPN until the key has been registered on the Freifunk Münsterland's servers. To register the key send it together with your node's name "
"(<em><%=pcdata(hostname)%></em>) to "
"<a href=\"mailto:info@freifunk-muensterland.de?subject=<%= urlencode('New Freifunk node ' .. hostname) %>&amp;"
"body=<%= urlencode('# ' .. hostname .. '\n' .. macaddr) %>\">info@freifunk-muensterland.de</a>."
"</p>"
"<div class=\"the-key\">"
" # <%= pcdata(hostname) %>"
" <br/>"
"<%= macaddr %>"
"</div>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>The node is currently rebooting and will try to connect to other nearby Freifunk nodes after that. Your can find lots of information about the Freifunk Münsterland community on <a href='http://freifunk-muensterland.de'>our homepage</a>. How did you hear about Freifunk? We would like to learn about your reasons for setting up a Freifunk router.</p> <p>Have fun with your node and explore the Freifunk network!</p>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:novpn"
msgstr ""
"<p>Warning! You left the VPN on this node disabled. This means, that it will only work, if it can reach another node via cable or wifi near by. If you want to share your own internet connection aswell, go back into configuration mode and enable VPN.</p>"

